questions.description:
Healthy rewards could entail:
1. Watching a movie
2. Taking a bath
3. Listening to music
4. Taking a nap
5. Buying myself flowers or a houseplant
6. Spending 15 minutes on social media
7. Taking a walk
8. Enjoying my favorite snack
9. Making my favorite meal
10. Going for a drive
11. Crossing the task off my to-do list
questions.title: I'll reward myself by...
If I’m not sure what to do, I’ll use these campus resources:

choices.title: Schedule a Let’s Talk session, a 20-minute mental health consultation
Call the Peer Access Line to talk with a peer, get support and learn about resources
Attend a Counseling and Consultation Service drop-in workshop to learn and practice mental health skills
Schedule a Wellness Coaching session to identify my strengths and set personal goals
Explore the Support tab to discover additional resources available
